â¢the effects of increased competition on our business;
â¢our ability to successfully expand in existing markets and successfully enter new markets;
â¢our ability to successfully integrate acquired technologies and businesses, including in the case of our acquisition of Wolt;
â¢changes in consumer behavior with respect to on-demand delivery;
â¢increases in marketing, sales, and other operating expenses that we may incur to grow and acquire new merchants, consumers, and Dashers;
â¢the mix among various aspects of our business, including our Marketplaces and Platform Services, our U.S.and non-U.S.","textTemplate":"","metadataSeparator":"
