{"id_":"2b777670-1a90-425a-9272-8ec98f3bbaaf","metadata":{"url":"https://www.streetinsider.com/SEC+Filings/Form+10-K+DoorDash%2C+Inc.+For%3A+Dec+31/22803975.html"},"excludedEmbedMetadataKeys":[],"excludedLlmMetadataKeys":[],"relationships":{"SOURCE":{"nodeId":"7ba4aa29-e118-4811-9eed-e4d9c8f2c5b6","metadata":{"url":"https://www.streetinsider.com/SEC+Filings/Form+10-K+DoorDash%2C+Inc.+For%3A+Dec+31/22803975.html"},"hash":"Z4ETa/gnzpEOW5Xc/RB8d06xUh9xe3gCAv/xq8kBSE0="},"PREVIOUS":{"nodeId":"f2898edd-8302-4795-bcd0-20e110650ae6","metadata":{"url":"https://www.streetinsider.com/SEC+Filings/Form+10-K+DoorDash%2C+Inc.+For%3A+Dec+31/22803975.html"},"hash":"ow9GoD9wE3apStx9ECsGd96wAitZ7ktAqeXZRpzKJzQ="},"NEXT":{"nodeId":"be113961-fe9b-4201-8a51-9c2945ac1251","metadata":{},"hash":"B/QYqIZae22t2VDHilQ7lxrGxzbGlIB8uk1ZuPf+cMU="}},"text":"In addition to other risk factors described elsewhere in this âRisk Factorsâ section, factors that may contribute to the variability of our quarterly and annual results include:
â¢our ability to attract and retain merchants, consumers, and Dashers that utilize our platform in a cost-effective manner;
â¢our ability to accurately forecast revenue and appropriately plan expenses;
